{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">C\u00e9l\u00e9bration solennelle de la P\u00e2que sous \u00c9z\u00e9chias<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-27: cf. (Za 1:3-6. \u00c9s 55:6, 7.) (No 9:1-14. Ex 12:1-29. 2 Ch 35:1-19.) 1 Co 5:8. Ph 3:1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias envoya des messagers dans tout Isra\u00ebl et Juda, et il \u00e9crivit aussi des lettres \u00e0 \u00c9phra\u00efm et \u00e0 Manass\u00e9, pour qu\u2019ils vinssent \u00e0 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem c\u00e9l\u00e9brer la P\u00e2que en l\u2019honneur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.2","name":"2 Chroniques 30:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.36","name":"2 Chroniques 29:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Le roi, ses chefs, et toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e avaient tenu conseil \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, afin que la P\u00e2que f\u00fbt c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e9e au second mois;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.3","name":"2 Chroniques 30:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.1","name":"2 Chroniques 30:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>car on ne pouvait la faire en son temps, parce que les sacrificateurs ne s\u2019\u00e9taient pas sanctifi\u00e9s en assez grand nombre et que le peuple n\u2019\u00e9tait pas rassembl\u00e9 \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.4","name":"2 Chroniques 30:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.2","name":"2 Chroniques 30:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>La chose ayant eu l\u2019approbation du roi et de toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.5","name":"2 Chroniques 30:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.3","name":"2 Chroniques 30:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>ils d\u00e9cid\u00e8rent de faire une publication dans tout Isra\u00ebl, depuis Beer-Sch\u00e9ba jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Dan, pour que l\u2019on v\u00eent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem c\u00e9l\u00e9brer la P\u00e2que en l\u2019honneur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Car elle n\u2019\u00e9tait plus c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e9e par la multitude comme il est \u00e9crit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.6","name":"2 Chroniques 30:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.4","name":"2 Chroniques 30:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Les coureurs all\u00e8rent avec les lettres du roi et de ses chefs dans tout Isra\u00ebl et Juda. Et, d\u2019apr\u00e8s l\u2019ordre du roi, ils dirent: Enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, revenez \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Abraham, d\u2019Isaac et d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, afin qu\u2019il revienne \u00e0 vous, reste \u00e9chapp\u00e9 de la main des rois d\u2019Assyrie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.7","name":"2 Chroniques 30:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.5","name":"2 Chroniques 30:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ne soyez pas comme vos p\u00e8res et comme vos fr\u00e8res, qui ont p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res, et qu\u2019il a livr\u00e9s \u00e0 la d\u00e9solation, comme vous le voyez.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.8","name":"2 Chroniques 30:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.6","name":"2 Chroniques 30:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ne raidissez donc pas votre cou, comme vos p\u00e8res; donnez la main \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, venez \u00e0 son sanctuaire qu\u2019il a sanctifi\u00e9 pour toujours, et servez l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, pour que sa col\u00e8re ardente se d\u00e9tourne de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.9","name":"2 Chroniques 30:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.7","name":"2 Chroniques 30:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Si vous revenez \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, vos fr\u00e8res et vos fils trouveront mis\u00e9ricorde aupr\u00e8s de ceux qui les ont emmen\u00e9s captifs, et ils reviendront dans ce pays; car l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, est compatissant et mis\u00e9ricordieux, et il ne d\u00e9tournera pas sa face de vous, si vous revenez \u00e0 lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.10","name":"2 Chroniques 30:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.8","name":"2 Chroniques 30:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Les coureurs all\u00e8rent ainsi de ville en ville dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm et de Manass\u00e9, et jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Zabulon. Mais on se riait et l\u2019on se moquait d\u2019eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.11","name":"2 Chroniques 30:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.9","name":"2 Chroniques 30:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Cependant quelques hommes d\u2019Aser, de Manass\u00e9 et de Zabulon s\u2019humili\u00e8rent et vinrent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.12","name":"2 Chroniques 30:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.10","name":"2 Chroniques 30:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Dans Juda aussi la main de Dieu se d\u00e9ploya pour leur donner un m\u00eame c\u0153ur et leur faire ex\u00e9cuter l\u2019ordre du roi et des chefs, selon la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.13","name":"2 Chroniques 30:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.11","name":"2 Chroniques 30:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Un peuple nombreux se r\u00e9unit \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem pour c\u00e9l\u00e9brer la f\u00eate des pains sans levain au second mois: ce fut une immense assembl\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.14","name":"2 Chroniques 30:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.12","name":"2 Chroniques 30:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Ils se lev\u00e8rent, et ils firent dispara\u00eetre les autels sur lesquels on sacrifiait dans J\u00e9rusalem et tous ceux sur lesquels on offrait des parfums, et ils les jet\u00e8rent dans le torrent de C\u00e9dron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.15","name":"2 Chroniques 30:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.13","name":"2 Chroniques 30:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ils immol\u00e8rent ensuite la P\u00e2que le quatorzi\u00e8me jour du second mois. Les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, saisis de confusion, s\u2019\u00e9taient sanctifi\u00e9s, et ils offrirent des holocaustes dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.16","name":"2 Chroniques 30:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.14","name":"2 Chroniques 30:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Ils occupaient leur place ordinaire, conform\u00e9ment \u00e0 la loi de Mo\u00efse, homme de Dieu, et les sacrificateurs r\u00e9pandaient le sang, qu\u2019ils recevaient de la main des L\u00e9vites.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.17","name":"2 Chroniques 30:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.15","name":"2 Chroniques 30:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Comme il y avait dans l\u2019assembl\u00e9e beaucoup de gens qui ne s\u2019\u00e9taient pas sanctifi\u00e9s, les L\u00e9vites se charg\u00e8rent d\u2019immoler les victimes de la P\u00e2que pour tous ceux qui n\u2019\u00e9taient pas purs, afin de les consacrer \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.18","name":"2 Chroniques 30:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.16","name":"2 Chroniques 30:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Car une grande partie du peuple, beaucoup de ceux d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, de Manass\u00e9, d\u2019Issacar et de Zabulon, ne s\u2019\u00e9taient pas purifi\u00e9s, et ils mang\u00e8rent la P\u00e2que sans se conformer \u00e0 ce qui est \u00e9crit. Mais \u00c9z\u00e9chias pria pour eux, en disant: Veuille l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui est bon, pardonner<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.19","name":"2 Chroniques 30:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.17","name":"2 Chroniques 30:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.19","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:19","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>\u00e0 tous ceux qui ont appliqu\u00e9 leur c\u0153ur \u00e0 chercher Dieu, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res, quoiqu\u2019ils n\u2019aient pas pratiqu\u00e9 la sainte purification!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.20","name":"2 Chroniques 30:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.18","name":"2 Chroniques 30:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.20","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:20","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel exau\u00e7a \u00c9z\u00e9chias, et il pardonna au peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.21","name":"2 Chroniques 30:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.19","name":"2 Chroniques 30:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.21","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:21","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Ainsi les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl qui se trouv\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e8rent la f\u00eate des pains sans levain, pendant sept jours, avec une grande joie; et chaque jour les L\u00e9vites et les sacrificateurs louaient l\u2019\u00c9ternel avec les instruments qui retentissaient en son honneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.22","name":"2 Chroniques 30:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.20","name":"2 Chroniques 30:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.22","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:22","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias parla au c\u0153ur de tous les L\u00e9vites, qui montraient une grande intelligence pour le service de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Ils mang\u00e8rent les victimes pendant sept jours, offrant des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, et louant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.23","name":"2 Chroniques 30:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.21","name":"2 Chroniques 30:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.23","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:23","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e fut d\u2019avis de c\u00e9l\u00e9brer sept autres jours. Et ils c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e8rent joyeusement ces sept jours;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.24","name":"2 Chroniques 30:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.22","name":"2 Chroniques 30:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.24","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:24","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>car \u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda, avait donn\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019assembl\u00e9e mille taureaux et sept mille brebis, et les chefs lui donn\u00e8rent mille taureaux et dix mille brebis, et des sacrificateurs en grand nombre s\u2019\u00e9taient sanctifi\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.25","name":"2 Chroniques 30:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.23","name":"2 Chroniques 30:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.25","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:25","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e de Juda, et les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, et tout le peuple venu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et les \u00e9trangers venus du pays d\u2019Isra\u00ebl ou \u00e9tablis en Juda, se livr\u00e8rent \u00e0 la joie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.26","name":"2 Chroniques 30:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.24","name":"2 Chroniques 30:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.26","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:26","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Il y eut \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem de grandes r\u00e9jouissances; et depuis le temps de Salomon, fils de David, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, rien de semblable n\u2019avait eu lieu dans J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.27","name":"2 Chroniques 30:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.25","name":"2 Chroniques 30:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.27","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 30:27","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.030.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.031.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.30.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites se lev\u00e8rent et b\u00e9nirent le peuple; et leur voix fut entendue, et leur pri\u00e8re parvint jusqu\u2019aux cieux, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la sainte demeure de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30","name":"2 Chroniques 30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30"}},"